If you have any problems, please contact us at support@ikonke.com.

Smart K offers the most comprehensive voice controlled smart home experience with Alexa. Control your plugs and other devices hands free. Just say it, Smart K will obey. 

Here’s a step by step instructions:
(1). Download our "Smart K" app in Google Play or IOS App Store;
(2). Launch the app and sign up a new account (or sign in if you’re already registered);
(3). Turn on Smart K devices and connect them with “Smart K” app;
(4). You can rename the devices with Smart K App. So if you rename a smart plug “fan”, then Echo dot will get that same name after discovered the devices in Step 10;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from Amazon Market, Google Play or IOS App Store, and connect Echo dot with "Alexa" app;
(6). Search the Alexa skills directory for "Smart K";
(7). Click Enable skill of "Smart K", then input your account username, password and region on the linking page;
(8). Talk to Echo dot “Alexa, discover devices”. Wait till Echo dot says "Discover is completed";
(9). Now all setup is done. Try talk to Echo dot to control your devices.

Here are part of the voice commands Smart K have:

Plugs:
* Alexa, turn on my plug
* Alexa, turn off my plug
